(born June 12, 1985) is an American television and movie actor. He is best known for his roles in 21 Jump Street, Charlie St. Cloud, Easy A, Fright Night, Now You See Me, Warm Bodies, Scrubs, and in Neighbors. He is the younger brother of actor James Franco and Tom Franco. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Santa Clara County, California Category:People from Palo Alto, California
